    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car! This has been such a reliable ride for me and it honestly still runs like a dream. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next owner to hit the road. If you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s been taken care of, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for this to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
