    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for optimized volumetric efficiency across the powerband. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, providing a mechanical connection to the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been addressed with a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural integrity under torque load, and the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings. While the aesthetic reflects its tenure on the road, the mechanical vitals\u2014including rod bearing service and valve clearances\u2014are current, ensuring this remains a precision instrument for the driving purist.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
