    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior features a stunning deep charcoal metallic finish that still holds a high-gloss shine, though you\u2019ll find the expected minor stone chips on the front fascia from highway commuting. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is trimmed in premium black leather; while the driver\u2019s seat shows light, natural creasing, the upholstery remains supple and free of tears. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, works exactly as it should. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health, having just undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and oil change. It shifts smoothly through all gears and provides a quiet, composed ride. With a complete service history and garage-kept storage, this car represents a fantastic value for a driver seeking a turn-key experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
